fielder Mike Marshall seems to trap a fly ball hit by Astro Billy Hatcher in 
the eighth inning (top), but when Marshall comes up with it (bottom), the 
umpires call it a catch. LORI SHEPLER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (San Diego 
County Edition) Glenn Davis 
</P>
