<P>
Actress Audrey Hepburn joined U.N. officials in Khartoum to see a Nile River 
barge depart for famine-threatened southern Sudan with 100 tons of food and 
medicine -- the first of more than 100,000 tons the United Nations hopes to 
ship to the war-torn region by month's end. The barge is expected to join 
